  <description><![CDATA[<p>Providing contemporary luxury since the start of the 19<sup>th</sup> century the Lido Palace is located on the edge of <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a> and surrounded by the dominant mountains and cliffs of <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a>. Once a resort for European royalty, the hotel is the definition of discreet luxury. Tranquil, refined interiors mix with eclectic contemporary furnishings in both public areas and guest rooms. </p>
<p>The CXI Spa is a state of the art facility offering a wide range of treatments as well as housing a fitness area. The vast spa area is complemented by both indoor and outdoor pools.</p>
<p>At the Il Re Della Busa restaurant, Chef Giuseppe Sestino has been awarded one Michelin star for his original flavours and international culinary experience. Tremani Bistrot offers Mediterranean gourmet while you enjoy the view of the gardens.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 45 mins by coach.</p>]]></description>
