  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Il Re della Busa</strong> is an elegant seafood restaurant with a fantastic lakeside location. Enjoy gourmet dinners in the romantic dining room or outside on the candlelit terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Tremani Bistrot</strong> is open for lunch and serves Mediterranean cuisine and light, healthy dishes.</p>
<p><strong>Balì Bar</strong> is open all day and is a great place to relax and enjoy a drink amongst the watercolour splashes on feature walls and Nouveau frescoes on the ceiling.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool</strong></span></p>
<p>Enjoy warm days in the sunshine next to Lido Palace’s beautiful outdoor pool, which is separated from the indoor pool by large floor-to-ceiling windows.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>CXI Centoundici SPA stretches over 1,500 square metres and boasts an indoor pool, Finnish sauna, salt room, three steam rooms and a small fitness area. A large choice of treatments are available (payable locally).</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free wifi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
