  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Premier Rooms</strong> are 35m² and have a modern style with views of the garden from the windows. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, free wifi, minbar, safe, hairdryer, bathrobes and slippers.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are 45m² and have views over the wooded grounds, the gardens and surrounding mountains from the windows.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are 35m² and have large windows with stunning views over the lake.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are 55m² offer a comfortable sitting area and views over the lake and surrounding mountains.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Junior Suites</strong> are 65m² have exceptional lake views from the floor-to-ceiling windows.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are also available on request, please call to book. These rooms are approximately 20m² and have garden views.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
